  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the risk factors and prediction biomarkers of chronic disease in adults aged
      35-74 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the risk factors and prediction biomarkers of chronic disease within adults
      aged 35-74 years in South China. Following up the incidence of major chronic disease
      including stroke, coronary heart disease, cancer, chronic obstructive pulmonary disease,
      diabetes and hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
